  "title": "NEW: Finance Director / Financial Controller (Construction/EPC)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Finance Director / Financial Controller</strong> for a <strong>newly created leadership role.</strong></p><p>Reporting directly to the CFO, you will lead the finance function across multiple high-value construction projects, with responsibility for project cost control, cash flow management, profitability analysis, and financial governance. <br /><br />You will work closely with the CFO, Managing Director, Project Directors, and Commercial teams to provide timely, accurate financial insights that support project delivery and business decision-making.</p><p>This is a high-impact, hands-on leadership role for a commercially minded finance professional who thrives in a project-driven environment. You will have the opportunity to shape financial strategy, build and develop a finance team, and play a key role in the continued growth of the business.</p><p><strong>Why this role is exciting:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Take ownership of a <strong>newly created finance leadership role</strong>, helping to define and strengthen the finance function.</p></li><li><p>Lead finance for a <strong>market-leading firm </strong>with a strong project pipeline.</p></li><li><p>Directly influence <strong>project profitability, cash flow, and strategic business decisions</strong>.<br /></p><p><strong>How to Apply</strong>: Click <strong>Apply Now</strong> — or send your resume directly to <a href=\"https://buildbridge-partners.careers-page.com/jobs/bd26b8d8-7789-4b7c-b3c2-54c6c190f255\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Talent@BuildBridgePartners.com</strong></a></p><p><br /><br /></p><p><br /><br /></p><p><br /><br /></p><p><strong>EA Details:</strong><br />EA Name: BuildBridge Partners Pte Ltd<br />EA License No: 25C2918<br />EA Reg No: R1551092 – Khoo Yan Jie</p></li></ul>",
